# Mainsail site — runtime configuration.
#
# Copy to `.env.local` to override. `.env.local` is gitignored.
#
# VITE_MANIFEST_URL points at the S3-published Mainsail manifest.
# When unset, the site falls back to the in-repo mock fixtures under
# public/mock-data/ so `npm run dev` works without S3 access (CLAUDE.md
# requires this).
#
# In production the manifest URL lives on the public S3 bucket (or the
# CloudFront distribution that fronts it). As of 2026-04-24 the Mainsail
# S3 bucket is still private — see mainsail_data/MILES.md §1 for the
# access model decision.
#
# Once the bucket is public / CDN-fronted, set:
# VITE_MANIFEST_URL=https://mainsail-public-data.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/manifest.json
